text: Gabriela Cândido (born ) is a Brazilian indoor volleyball player. She is a current member of the Brazil women's national volleyball team. ==Career== She participated at the 2015 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship and 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's U23 World Championship. ==Clubs== * SESC Rio (2015–2016) * SESI São Paulo (2016–2017) * Vôlei Bauru (2017–2020) * Osasco Voleibol Clube (2020–) ==Awards== ===National team=== * 2013 16px FIVB U18 World Championship * 2015 16px FIVB U20 World Championship ==References== ==External links== * FIVB Biography Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian women's volleyball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
